## Détails d’implémentation (pratico-pratique)

### 1) Signature de la commande

```java
record StartReviewCommand(String reviewExternalId, String partyId, Map<String,Object> attrs) {}
```

### 2) Orchestration « single-call » (pseudo-code)

```java
@Transactional(noRollbackFor = ProgressSaved.class)
public void process(StartReviewCommand cmd) {
  var review = reviewManager.openOrGet(cmd.partyId(), cmd.reviewExternalId()); // UQ "one active"

  var work = workRepo.loadOrInit(review.id(), cmd.partyId());
  int pageSize = config.familyPageSize(); // ex. 100
  int page = work.lastMemberIdx() / pageSize;

  while (true) {
    var members = familyClient.fetchPage(cmd.partyId(), page, pageSize);
    if (members.isEmpty()) break;

    processChunk(review, members, work);   // fait ses propres mini-transactions
    work = workRepo.markProgress(work, (page+1)*pageSize);
    page++;
  }

  workRepo.markDone(work);
}
```

### 3) Traitement d’un chunk (transactions **courtes**)

```java
@Transactional
void processChunk(Review review, List<Member> members, ReviewWork work) {
  var blockOps = new ArrayList<BlockUpsertOp>();

  for (Member m : members) {
    var plan = rolePolicy.resolveBlocksFor(m.roles());
    for (BlockKind kind : plan.inScope()) {
      var op = blocks.createOrReuseApprovedCurrent(review, m.partyId(), kind);
      if (op.isNewOrChanged()) {
        blockOps.add(op.toUpsertMessage()); // à pousser vers SF
      }
    }
  }

  outboxWriter.enqueueBatch(blockOps);  // écriture outbox (dedupe key stable)
}
```

### 4) SCD2 + Gate (sans événements)

```java
Optional<BlockVersion> createOrReuseApprovedCurrent(Review review, String partyId, BlockKind kind) {
  var block = blockRepo.findOrCreate(partyId, kind);
  var current = blockRepo.loadCurrentVersion(block.id());

  if (current != null && !current.state().isApproved()) {
    metrics.increment("gate_noop", "kind", kind.name());
    return Optional.empty(); // réutilisé par la review via REVIEW_TARGET si besoin
  }

  // historiser l’ancienne version si existante
  if (current != null) blockRepo.closeVersion(current.id(), now());

  // créer v+1
  var next = blockRepo.createVersion(block.id(), current == null ? 1 : current.versionNo() + 1, initialState(kind));
  blockRepo.setCurrent(block.id(), next.id());
  reviewTargetRepo.attach(review.id(), next.id(), partyId, subjectRole(review, partyId));
  return Optional.of(next);
}
```

