## Petits croquis (pour aligner)

### Séquence (synchrone, sans événements internes)

```plantuml
@startuml
actor iHub
participant "HitService" as HIT
participant "ReviewManager" as REV
participant "FamilyClient" as FAM
participant "BlockManager" as BLK
database "DB" as DB
queue "Outbox→SF" as OUT

iHub -> HIT: process(startReviewCmd)
HIT -> REV: openOrGet(party)
REV --> HIT: reviewId
loop pages
  HIT -> FAM: fetch(page,size)
  FAM --> HIT: members[]
  HIT -> BLK: createOrReuseApprovedCurrent(reviewId, members)
  BLK -> DB: batch SCD2 + attach review
  BLK --> HIT: upsertMessages[]
  HIT -> OUT: enqueue(upsertMessages)  ' asynchrone uniquement ici
end
HIT --> iHub: 200 OK (workId)
@enduml
```

